Client HOW-TO:
1. Open file "LumaEmu.ini" and change "CHANGEME" by your nickname, save it.
2. Launch "Rust Client.exe"
3. After game loading, push F1 and write on commandline : net.connect ip_adress:port (change ip_adress and port to the ip adress and port of hoster/server, default port is 28015)
4. Push Enter and play.
During the client launch you can use this commands : http://playrustwiki.com/wiki/Controls_and_Commands#Commands (commands server can be use if you are login on administrator : rcon.login "password")

Server HOW-TO:
1. Launch "Rust Server.exe" (and not rust_server.exe)
You can be change a part of configuration on cfg/server.cfg
During the server launch you can config it with this commands: https://developer.valvesoftware.com/wiki/Rust
